Output demo.gif

Set Shell bash
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set FontSize 16
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "npm start"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Show

Type "Hello world! "
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Type "This is promptpad "
Sleep 300ms
Type "- a minimal terminal text editor."
Sleep 1s

Enter
Enter
Type "It tracks lines, characters, and tokens."
Sleep 1s


# Type fast to show the waveform
Type@50ms " Let me type quickly to demo it..."
Sleep 2s
